data.description: PRICED TO SELL! This LARGE Marquise Model villa features 3 BEDROOM, 2 BATHROOMS and a 2 CAR GARAGE with UTILITY SINK. The LARGE EAT-IN KITCHEN has PLANTATION SHUTTERS on the WINDOW, STAINLESS-STEEL APPLIANCES and LOTS OF STORAGE. VAULTED CEILINGS. SPLIT FLOOR PLAN provides privacy for you and your guests. LARGE WALK-IN CLOSET in the Master Bedroom. The Master Bathroom sports DUAL SINKS, VANITY, WALK-IN SHOWER and ROMAN TUB. FRONT-LOAD WASHER & DRYER. FULL ACCORDION SHUTTERS. NEWER HOT WATER HEATER. TILED, SCREENED PATIO. DON'T DELAY or you will miss out.Majestic Isles is a community that offers care-free, resort-style living at its best! The 16,000 square foot clubhouse features an Olympic-size heated swimming pool and Jacuzzi. The fitness center has the latest cardiovascular equipment, weights and treadmills.  There is a multi-purpose room for parties and gatherings. With a billiards room, ceramics room, several card rooms, library, and a full array of clubs, you will never be bored! Outside adjacent to the clubhouse are 4 champion Har-Tru tennis courts and a shuffleboard court. Convenient access to I-95 and the Florida Turnpike. Close to shopping and wonderful restaurants.
